    "7402542": {
        "Desc": "",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "Caterpillar",
                    "T": "Sorry for the delay. About the way I said I got the Coupons earlier..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "What did you do to him?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Someone that aggressive doesn't seem like the type to take advice from anyone. Why would he give up so easily...?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Caterpillar",
                    "T": "Just a few small tricks."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Caterpillar",
                    "T": "\"The culprit is where he should be.\" This is an undeniable fact."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Caterpillar",
                    "T": "Making someone as straightforward as him \"certain\" of an undeniable fact isn't exactly hard."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Like that time with Julien?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Caterpillar",
                    "T": "That's right. Just like that time with Julien."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Caterpillar",
                    "T": "I've been here for a long time, as you know. After staying in one place for a long time, it's only natural to pick up a few handy tricks to exert some degree of influence over your environment."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Almost too handy, I'd say."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Sounds a little suspicious..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Changing a stubborn person's mind with just a few simple phrases almost sounds like magic... Could there have been times when we were also influenced by magic without even knowing it?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Considering how pure-hearted you are, Paimon, that is a worrying thought."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "#You, too, {NICKNAME}! Wait a minute... You're not saying Paimon's as gullible as Julien, are you?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Would someone even realize that they're being influenced?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Hmm... Paimon was already a bit sleepy, but now her head is totally spinning..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Caterpillar",
                    "T": "It's not as simple as it looks — There are always limits to the application of tricks like these, and the results aren't always what you'd hoped for."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Caterpillar",
                    "T": "It's like with Julien — He always had a knack for art, but he lacked confidence because of his visual impairment. The \"certainty\" that he could draw well was inside him to begin with."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Caterpillar",
                    "T": "But in other cases, the concept of \"certainty\" is just too abstract, making it difficult to predict the outcome."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Caterpillar",
                    "T": "So, I did take a chance this time. I just thought that if he held us up here, it would keep delaying the plan to get Lanoire out of the Fortress..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Caterpillar",
                    "T": "Besides, I doubt you wanted to be questioned by him repeatedly either."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "You shouldn't take chances like that."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Well, you've got to take chances to achieve your goals."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Caterpillar",
                    "T": "You're absolutely right."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Caterpillar",
                    "T": "Back to the matter at hand... If you've changed your mind and want to back out, I understand completely. Lanoire might be sad for a time though. For her, playmates like you are hard to come by."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Hmm... We've already made a promise to her, so we can't just go back on our word now. Right?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "A promise is a promise."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Yeah. Consider this our way of helping her out!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "This doesn't mean I trust you."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Caterpillar",
                    "T": "Of course. Knowing that our goals are aligned for the time being is enough."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Speaking of which, where is she?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Caterpillar",
                    "T": "She went on an adventure early this morning — probably to rehearse for what's to come after she leaves this place. It's just as well, I have a few headaches to go take care of soon..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Caterpillar",
                    "T": "You can usually get a reward for helping others — including the guards — take care of some headaches."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Oh, we totally get that. Sounds just like some of the Adventurers' Guild's commissions."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Caterpillar",
                    "T": "I see. Would you two join me on this next commission, then?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Sure! Where are we going?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Caterpillar",
                    "T": "The abandoned production zone in the lower levels."
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
