    "7402516": {
        "Desc": "Listen to the noise box",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "Lanoire",
                    "T": "Phew, guess our adventure's almost at an end. The Coupon Cafeteria's our final stop."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "So the ultimate destination of adventuring is a good meal."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Not bad, right? Adventures take a toll on your body, so eating afterward is a must."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Lanoire",
                    "T": "That's right! And I've never seen someone as small as Ms. Paimon! You're even smaller than Ms. Sigewinne. You should eat more, so you can grow bigger!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "I think Paimon's fine just the way she is."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Paimon thinks so, too!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "The thought of Paimon growing up... Ugh, that gives me a headache."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Ugh, you're probably thinking about something rude right now, aren't you?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Lanoire",
                    "T": "By the way, do the two of you have any Coupons?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Um, Paimon doesn't think so..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Well, that means we get no food. Oops."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Lanoire",
                    "T": "No, don't worry! Just talk to Bran, and you'll get a yummy free meal!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Lanoire",
                    "T": "Bran's the clockwork meka over there. It was broken, but Wolsey repaired it."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Lanoire",
                    "T": "You only get a free meal once per day, though, and you won't know what you'll get. The best thing you can get is the Tasses Ragout."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Wait, you won't know what you'll get? Why can't you order what you want?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Lanoire",
                    "T": "Wolsey says that it's meant to be both a surprise and a risk precisely 'cause it's a free meal. If you don't want any risks, then you've gotta use Coupons."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Lanoire",
                    "T": "Will the two of you try the free meal?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Paimon will give it a try! Paimon is always lucky, and this stuff's free! How can free meals be bad?"
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
