    "7402620": {
        "Desc": "Talk to Caterpillar",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Huh? Why is it off again?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "The Fontaine Research Institute's tech really is unreliable..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Did it malfunction? At least it won't explode this time... probably."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Caterpillar",
                    "T": "Maybe someone's catching up to us..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Someone sent to catch us?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Caterpillar",
                    "T": "Maybe."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Sh—Should we go back and take a look then?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Noailles",
                    "T": "No need to trouble yourselves, esteemed guests."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Noailles",
                    "T": "You're evil, and I represent the side of justice... Even without Gardemeks, I won't let you get away..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Noailles",
                    "T": "Lay down your arms and surrender!"
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
    "7402621": {
        "Desc": "Defeat Noailles",
        "Talk": []
    },
    "7402622": {
        "Desc": "Talk to Noailles",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "Noailles",
                    "T": "He's... He's just a monster! Why would you help him? Why would anyone help him?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Lanoire",
                    "T": "Cater isn't a monster! Why... Why would you call him that, evil sorcerer...?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Lanoire",
                    "T": "Ever since Mother left Meropide, Cater's been really nice to me, he's never lied to me..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Lanoire",
                    "T": "There are other nice people here too... but none of them are as nice as Cater. He tells me all kinds of stories, and listens to mine, too..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Lanoire",
                    "T": "I won't let you call him a monster!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Noailles",
                    "T": "Why? Justice should triumph over evil..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Estienne",
                    "T": "There's no such thing as good or evil here."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Estienne! What are you doing here?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "You're late."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Estienne",
                    "T": "So sorry about that."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "What are you doing here?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Estienne",
                    "T": "\"Atoning for my sins,\" of course."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Estienne",
                    "T": "It took me quite some time to retrieve those Gardemeks he utilized without authorization. Well done, you didn't just break the rules, but also violated regulations."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Estienne",
                    "T": "Now it's your turn to accept your punishment. You're coming back with me."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Estienne",
                    "T": "As for you guys... If you want to leave, this is your last chance. *sigh* With all the fuss he's been making, who knows what will happen later."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Estienne",
                    "T": "Of course, it's also possible that nothing will happen at all."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Caterpillar",
                    "T": "Thank you."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Estienne",
                    "T": "If you really want to thank me, don't come back again."
                },
                {
                    "N": "???",
                    "T": "Then, with Estienne's help, the path is reopened..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Paimon guesses we can go now... We should be in the clear now, right? Hm... Let's get a move on before we run into any more surprises!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Lanoire",
                    "T": "We're leaving Meropide again? Will we ever come back?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Sure, if we do something bad out there."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Lanoire",
                    "T": "Oh, then..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Hey! Don't go running off causing trouble just to come back for a visit!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "We'll use the front door next time."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Going through the regular channels is safer."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Lanoire",
                    "T": "Well then, goodbye, Meropide."
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
